title: SMNTY Classics: The Ballad of Dolly Parton
itunes:title: SMNTY Classics: The Ballad of Dolly Parton
description:
To celebrate her January 20 birthday and her current involvement in a possible COVID-19 vaccine, Cristen and Caroline look at the incredible life of country music legend Dolly Parton and why many consider the over-the-top entertainer a feminist icon in this classic episode.
